data.description: Need space? Look no further! This georgous home has expansive space on the interior and the exterior, all in a great location!  This home features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, with new windows, plantation shutters, and blinds throughout. The main level features the living room with hardwood floors, kitchen with granite countertops and built in pantry, gas stove, and a beautiful sunroom off to the side which leads to the first deck that overlooks the backyard. The upper level has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The primary suite has large windows which makes the room light and airy. The primary bathroom has a large shower and upgraded fixtures. The two additional rooms which share a bathroom finish off the top level of the home. From the living room you can go down a few stairs to another finished level which contains a 4th bedroom and 3rd full bathroom, a bonus room, and the laundry room. This also leads outside to the covered area with a large hot tub. The steps then lead to a well maintained pool with deck and gazebo. The backyard is level and fenced. This home doesn't stop there! Inside, down a few more stairs you will find the 2 car garage and partially finished basement space with raised storage area. Outside of the home, level with the garage, there is a 24' x 48' building/workshop and covered area for more parking. Lots of storage and possiblities! No HOA. Newer roof with 30 year architectural shingles and septic serviced in 2020. Award winnning school system and a location that is close to Lake Allatoona with hiking, biking, and water sports. I575, and I75 are only a few miles away. Many shopping and dining choices.
